  "semantic_description": "Scans a null-terminated CSV string of signed decimal integers, parses each token in place without modifying the buffer, and returns the minimum parsed value. The implementation uses sequential character-scanning loops for optional sign, digit accumulation, comma skipping, and repeated token parsing until the terminating zero byte.",
